  "texts": [
    "Similarly, Etminani et al. (2022) proposed a 3D DL model that employs fluorine 18 fluorodeoxyglucose PET scans for predicting ultimate clinical diagnosis of dementia and AD.",
    "The diagnostic outcomes predicted by this model demonstrate a commendable performance in comparison to human readers and their collective agreement.",
    "The 3D CNN model is constructed utilizing the VGG16 CNN architecture.",
    "It is implemented using the Keras on a system running the Ubuntu 18.09 OS and equipped with an NVIDIA Quadra GV100 GPU.",
    "It achieves a validation accuracy of 78.9%."
  ],
